| Input Name | Expected Slug |
|-----------|---------------|
| `"My App"` | `"my-app"` |
| `"Next.js Blog"` | `"next-js-blog"` |
| `"---"` | `"project"` |
| `"Hello World 123"` | `"hello-world-123"` |
